CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 25, 1963, pg. 6 reads: "For 50 Years - Mrs. W.W. Gittens (left) is shown presenting gifts to Mrs. Helane Pryor Wilson of Bluefield, W.Va.; Mrs. Iva Johnson of Steelton, Pa., and Mrs. William Dix of McKeesport. The trio, graduates of McKeesport High School, class of 1913, was feted at a party last Saturday afternoon at the Gittens home.  They attended the reunion banquet later the same night.  The party was co-sponsored by members of the Semper Fidelis Club and Iota Phi Lambda Sorority. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. W.W. Gittens, presenting gifts to Helane Pryor Wilson, Iva Johnson, and Mrs. William Dix during party held in the Gittens home
